NCP_Fault
---------

        NAME
         NCP_Fault -- return localized NCP error string
     
        SYNOPSIS
         NCP_Fault( code, header, buffer, buffersize );
                    D0     A0      A1        D1
     
        void NCP_Fault( LONG, STRPTR, STRPTR, ULONG );
     
